OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start, with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of light rain and drizzle at
OL,7,Ftimes, especially over western hills.
OL,8,FBecoming mostly dry into the afternoon
OL,9,Fwith some bright or sunny spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping, especially in the east.
OL,11,FFeeling noticeably milder. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRather cloudy with some
OL,14,Fdrizzle on western hills. Elsewhere,
OL,15,Fit will be a dry night with some clear
OL,16,Fspells, especially in the east.
OL,17,FLocally chilly in rural spots. Light
OL,18,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
