OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,6,Fdrizzle on western hills. The cloud
OL,7,Fshould break up to give some bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells into the afternoon. Rain
OL,9,Freaching northern areas by evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FLargely dry with bright or sunny
OL,13,Fspells Thursday. Feeling cooler.
OL,14,FBecoming unsettled with spells of wet
OL,15,Fand windy weather on Friday and
OL,16,FSaturday. Risk of gales. Temperatures
OL,17,Fnear average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
